 existing literature. In\nparticular, as the singlet-Higgs coupling lambda increases, vacuum stability\nbecomes more serious of an issue.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Sep 2012 20:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Jan 2013 17:27:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
