ution of the\ncluster galaxies. We conclude that A520 shows no evidence to contradict the\ncollisionless dark matter scenario.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Sep 2012 20:19:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
