 a semi-analytic model for the reionization history,\nwe infer that approximately half of the ionizing photons needed to complete\nreionization have already been observed in star-forming galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Sep 2012 03:48:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
