s a potential shaping force of genome regulation and organization.\nThis is reflected in the use of different control strategies at genes with\ndifferent sets of functional constraints.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Sep 2012 10:15:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-09-12"}
