incipal bundles over the worldsheet with a structural action groupoid\nbased on the target space. Finally, the large gauge anomaly is identified with\nthe obstruction to the existence of topological defect networks implementing\nthe action of the gauge group of the gauged sigma model and those giving a\nlocal trivialisation of a gauge bundle of an arbitrary topology over the\nworldsheet.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Sep 2012 14:41:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-09-12"}
